<a class="heading-toc" id="digital-tv-broadcast-reception"></a> <h3 id="mntl-sc-block_2-0-44" class="comp mntl-sc-list-item-title mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> Digital TV Broadcast Reception </span> </h3>
<figure id="mntl-sc-block_2-0-45" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-image figure-landscape figure-high-res">
